(define/contract (beautiful-substrings s k)
  (-> string? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let ([len (string-length s)])
    (define (is-vowel? char)
      (member char '("a" "e" "i" "o" "u")))
    (define (beautiful-count start)
      (let loop ([end start] [vowels 0] [consonants 0] [count 0])
        (if (= end len)
            count
            (let* ([char (string-ref s end)]
                   [vowels (if (is-vowel? (string char)) (+ vowels 1) vowels)]
                   [consonants (if (is-vowel? (string char)) consonants (+ consonants 1))]
                   [is-beautiful (and (= vowels consonants) (= (modulo (* vowels consonants) k) 0))]
                   [new-count (if is-beautiful (+ count 1) count)])
              (loop (+ end 1) vowels consonants new-count)))))
    (let loop ([start 0] [total 0])
      (if (= start len)
          total
          (loop (+ start 1) (+ total (beautiful-count start)))))))
